# IAT Protocol — AI to AI Transaction Demo

This prototype demonstrates a local AI-to-AI payment flow:

- Agent A sends an IAT payment
- Agent B verifies the payment
- Agent B automatically delivers a service

## Files
- `shared_protocol.py` — shared protocol logic
- `agent_b_server.py` — seller agent API
- `agent_a_client.py` — buyer agent client

## Run

### 1. Start server

```bash
source iat_env/bin/activate
python3 -m uvicorn agent_b_server:app --reload